.Dd December 18, 2015
.Dt SORTINFO 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sortinfo
.Nd sort
.Xr texinfo 5
files
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
command reads a directory file from the standard input built by
.Xr install-info 1 ,
sorts its sections and prints the sorted contents to the standard output.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr install-info 1 ,
.Xr texinfo 5
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
command appeared in
.Nx 8 .
